# Format for ~/.config/setup-sync/sanitize-map.txt (used by sync-from-live.sh).
# The REAL map is machine-local and must NEVER be committed to this repo —
# committing it would reveal the very names it scrubs. Recreate it on a new
# machine from the private Obsidian vault notes.
#
# Tab-separated: pattern<TAB>replacement
# Applied top-to-bottom, case-insensitive, substring match.
# Put the most specific patterns FIRST (acmecorp.com before acmecorp).
acmecorp.com	example.com
acmecorp	project-a
clientb-portal	portal-1
clientb	project-b
jdoe	user
